```plantuml
@startuml caraml-dev_turing

actor User

box "Turing Platform" #LightBlue
    participant "API Server" as API
    participant "Router Manager" as RouterMgr
    participant "Ensembler Manager" as EnsemblerMgr
    participant "Experiment Engine" as ExpEngine
    participant "Batch Ensembling Job Manager" as BatchMgr
    participant "Alerting System" as AlertSys
    participant "Logging & Monitoring" as LogMon
    participant "Infrastructure Controller" as InfraCtrl
end box

User -> API: Initiate API Request
API -> RouterMgr: Manage Router Request
RouterMgr -> ExpEngine: (Optional) Execute Experiment
ExpEngine --> RouterMgr: Experiment Result
RouterMgr -> EnsemblerMgr: Manage Ensembler Request
EnsemblerMgr -> BatchMgr: Submit Batch Job
BatchMgr -> InfraCtrl: Deploy Spark Job on Kubernetes
InfraCtrl -> BatchMgr: Job Deployment Status
BatchMgr -> EnsemblerMgr: Job Completion Status
EnsemblerMgr --> RouterMgr: Ensembler Response
RouterMgr -> API: Router Response
API --> User: API Response

API -> AlertSys: Trigger Alert
AlertSys --> API: Alert Confirmation

API -> LogMon: Log Request
LogMon --> API: Log Confirmation

@enduml
```